channel.title: [Looking For] Development team-
channel.description:
Hey guys,
I am currently looking for a development team to work with, i would like the team to be done 65%+ Server sided, this would intern make my job easier... I would also like the team to be mature, (In other words not a bunch of little kids) Preferably 15+ and i would like the team to look like it is going somewhere... And the server should already have fund's to go toward development. Also i would prefer the revision 500+
Now here is what i have to offer: I am a Web Developer, i have been developing website's for about 6 years now. I have an un-used VBulletin 4.1.4 license. I am willing to be pretty much anyones web developer, considering the above term's are met. If you need a web developer, and would like to take me up on this offer and welcome me into your team please either reply to the post or send me a PM and we can discuss further. Please add my MSN: Schitzomniac@hotmail.ca
Best regards, ~Justin
